name: Variability of light
description:
2480x3508px
8 sec

Oneday while I spend relax time on my bed,It's a really good day with soft light from the outside of the window with my plant in my bedroom.Then in the afternoon rain has coming with black clound and the light is decreasing until turn my bedroom in to the dark.After twenty min the rain had gone and the light become increasing and more blighter than in the morning. Everythings that happen in only oneday and make me realize about the beautiful of emotional of the light.
